Houghton Mifflin Harcourt - Wikipedia






















 






Houghton Mifflin Harcourt

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Houghton Mifflin Harcourt




Parent company
Vivendi (2001–2002)


Traded as
NASDAQ: HMHC
