Be Curious. Discover what’s possible.
Spark a lifelong love of learning with us.




















Curiosity is essential to lifelong learning. At Houghton Mifflin Harcourt, we aim to spark a lifelong love of learning in every individual we touch.


Featured Career Areas


‹
›





Technology
Develop and influence vital technology decisions around our product lines.



Sales
Engage educators with solutions comprised of HMH products and services.



Consumer
Join us to produce engaging content and experiences for lifelong learners.



Heinemann
Help create professional development resources for teachers in grades K-20.





Product Development & Marketing
Drive awareness of products and services through development & marketing.



Corporate
Find opportunities in finance, corporate affairs, facilities, legal and HR groups.



Global Supply Chain
Join a team focused on manufacturing operations, distribution and delivery.



Professional Services
Provide product or technology training to teachers and district personnel.





Trade
Help us publish some of the world’s most renowned books in various formats.



Technology
Develop and influence vital technology decisions around our product lines.



Sales
Engage educators with solutions comprised of HMH products and services.



Consumer
Join us to produce engaging content and experiences for lifelong learners.






